3/1/2011
- Adds in a library for handling ini files as well as a routine for handling
  ini settings.
- Adds in a default ini file to show how it works
- Updates README file to show how settings.ini works

2/16/2011
- Adds in a serial Alpha Beta search method. Note that this search method is
  not yet working with OpenMP and is serial.
- Slight changes to README file and added a CHANGELIST

